,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1397a211d723d3d14ea00d5012493596d7f3b4d5","tid":1869864,"uid":621,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"05d4cd231c8ce02f37302239ebdeee7958bc8a9a","tid":1869864,"uid":306000,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T13:11:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好唔想無咗而家同佢日日傾計嘅時光<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好唔想見到佢日後同另一個人都咁樣相處<br />\n好唔想...無咗佢<br />\n仲好想繼續了解佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T13:15:26.000Z","msg":"同你諗法一樣<br />\n但佢已經唔理我喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我可以點"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T13:22:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T13:24:04.000Z","msg":"我唔想行呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好想佢返轉頭搵我"},{"pid":"db63273083e5d6bb4a553725ecd208cad44f348c","tid":1869864,"uid":158391,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T13:28:25.000Z","msg":"每個人都想對方搵自己先<br />\n但自己需盡力瘋狂去搵對方，去做愛做的事<br />\n無憾<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83aee64c175a8f730ecc8508d7c21612ebcc28f4","tid":1869864,"uid":276783,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T13:32:38.000Z","msg":"會成日諗住佢  <br />\n會想像一齊左之後既情境   <br />\n會想對佢好 <br />\n會關心佢<br />\n對住佢個陣可能會表現得唔自然<br />\n會介意佢對自己既睇法<br />\n會想知佢有無鐘意既對象<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33f97013c82df12559276fc721382f93c377bb66","tid":1869864,"uid":293845,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T13:41:56.000Z","msg":"個人而言，無得失好壞計算或意識之時？例如一種缺點，喺另一個人身上出現我就察覺到呢個缺點我唔中意而扣分時我知係好感，心中會有個天秤知佢身上有嘢我中意，但同時有嘢我唔接受。但同一個缺點嘅特質喺我真係中意嗰人都有相同問題時，我完全無咁意識，只覺得有咁缺點好可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d04fa3fe34f353b1be6527cd02b9776e7eb8ec2b","tid":1869864,"uid":293845,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"64c24a3c194144e93a5ecdf99c02ce41a66639a2","tid":1869864,"uid":306000,"like":11,"dislike":3,"score":8,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T12:36:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我係想同佢傾計<br />\n都想/鍾意佢關心我<br />\n期待同佢講電話<br />\n<br />\n我又覺得自己唔係鍾意佢<br />\n但我又鍾意同佢一齊<br />\n可能只係友誼上嘅喜歡？鍾意同佢咩都講到？又或者純粹鍾意佢鍾意我？<br />\n<br />\n但我又覺得自己無咁膚淺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我都唔知道"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T13:45:16.000Z","msg":"咁我覺仲係好感。我身邊有個人都每個星期見到日，會好期待見面同一齊玩會好多嘢傾，某日突然之間我都有諗過下係咪在意，但又清晰地知唔想一齊嘅卻步原因，所以覺只係志同道合而咁啱呢排陪得多而已。"},{"pid":"76ddd0cb406e121ce31bae7c6c99fa88dbaaf0f1","tid":1869864,"uid":90269,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c155cd2545375727bbabb654140b2be5dd5409f3","tid":1869864,"uid":621,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa4582aad5eb9ff51d76b22890b870677f8edec6","tid":1869864,"uid":306000,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1397a211d723d3d14ea00d5012493596d7f3b4d5","tid":1869864,"uid":621,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T13:15:26.000Z","msg":"同你諗法一樣<br />\n但佢已經唔理我喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我可以點"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T13:22:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T13:24:04.000Z","msg":"我唔想行呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好想佢返轉頭搵我"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T14:46:22.000Z","msg":"點解唔理你？"},{"pid":"b9c8e4f7e51191883151721174ffe176059ba7b5","tid":1869864,"uid":621,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"76ddd0cb406e121ce31bae7c6c99fa88dbaaf0f1","tid":1869864,"uid":90269,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c1